ZH: 今天晚上我亲手做了晚饭。
EN: I cooked dinner myself tonight.
ZH: 她作为画家，亲手创作了这幅美丽的画。
EN: As an artist, she personally created this beautiful painting.
ZH: 爸爸亲手修好了水龙头。
EN: Dad personally fixed the faucet.
ZH: 我亲手制作了这个生日蛋糕。
EN: I personally made this birthday cake.
ZH: 妈妈亲手缝了一条裙子给我。
EN: Mom sewed a dress for me herself.
ZH: 他亲手砍下了那棵大树。
EN: He personally chopped down that big tree.
ZH: 我亲手将那封信投入邮箱。
EN: I personally put that letter into the mailbox.
ZH: 她用亲手织的围巾给我送来。
EN: She brought me a scarf that she knitted herself.
ZH: 作为厨师，他亲手烹制了这顿美食。
EN: As a chef, he cooked this delicious meal himself.
ZH: 我亲手帮她修好了自行车。
EN: I personally fixed her bike for her.
ZH: 奶奶亲手制作了这个漂亮的毛衣。
EN: Grandma personally made this beautiful sweater.
ZH: 这是我亲手栽种的花园。
EN: This is the garden I planted myself.
ZH: 他亲手为我写了一封感谢信。
EN: He personally wrote me a thank-you letter.
ZH: 我亲手收集了这些鲜花送给你。
EN: I personally collected these flowers to give to you.
ZH: 姐姐亲手画了一张漂亮的明信片。
EN: My sister personally drew a beautiful postcard.
ZH: 在家种的蔬菜比超市购买的更好吃，我亲手种的。
EN: The vegetables grown at home taste better than the ones bought from the supermarket because I grew them myself.
ZH: 他亲手搭建了一个小屋用于周末度假。
EN: He personally built a cabin for weekend getaways.
ZH: 经过一段时间的努力，他亲手打造了一支成功的团队。
EN: After a period of hard work, he personally built a successful team.
ZH: 我亲手给这些书籍装订上了标签。
EN: I personally labeled these books myself.
ZH: 孩子们亲手制作了贺卡送给老师。
EN: The children personally made greeting cards to give to their teacher.
